A very important part of running a football team is preparing a gameplan. 

The goal here is to set offensive and defensive strategies. 

                    Percentage Model

  Offensive Strategies:
    Choose your play style; 
      Pass Heavy:
          In a pass heavy offensive gameplan, all WRs will get a 10% bonus to their scores. 
      Run Heavy:
          In a run heavy offensive gameplan, all RBs will get a 10% bonus to their ssores.
      Balanced:
          All WRs and RBs will receive a 5% bonus to their scores. 
          
   Defensive Strategies
      Play Style;
        Zone:
          Set your defensive players to matchup against a specific slot in the depth chart.
        Man:
          Set your defensive players to matchup against a specific player on an opponent's team. 
